    "He took a conservative stance on cleaning of pictures, regarding aggressive cleaning as an act of vandalism.": [],
    "He was also forthright about his duty to curry favor for donations.": [],
    "''In the United States,'' he wrote in his autobiography, ''it is axiomatic that the undertaker and the museum director arrive almost simultaneously.": [],
